list.name: Changes
list.comment: Many changes. 1. myUtils.py - removed unnecessary code that prints classnames of objectDetectionModel. 2. objectDetection.py - commented code that will apply green box and text on image frame. 3. main.py - added keys functionality for 't' and 'q' for toggle alarm mode and ending process. 4. firebase.py - corrected image name while calling image_url(). changed the Notification triggering code. and more 5. messageTrigger.py - cleared bug when calling send_message(). now messages will trigger without initial waiting time.
